{"tid":2285891,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"拜登他都坐不穩  要等～","createTime":"2020-11-14T13:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T05:01:05.000Z","uid":70786,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b22d01f167db388ffab055b944cd7e235ed13604","tid":2285891,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:19:57.000Z","msg":"拜登他都坐不穩   要等～<br />\n<br />\n自知侵侵咬得緊   嚇到手震<br />\n<br />\n然後又扮晒逼真   佢冇得瞓<br />\n<br />\n自稱當選搵老襯　我侵不應該再忍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傻登   明明缺選票<br />\n<br />\n仍然慶祝 叫又跳<br />\n<br />\n架已丟　或者就快不能了<br />\n<br />\n美國信心崩潰了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n＊登登喊驚了　好彩有燈蕭<br />\n<br />\n　(賓州痛失了　只好喊通宵)<br />\n<br />\n　或者　當初你應搵燒山高照<br />\n<br />\n　你會早已搵得夠選票<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　左膠慶祝了　不好意思打擾<br />\n<br />\n　或者　應該親口請你快走了<br />\n<br />\n　好走了　讓你知道<br />\n<br />\n　美夢完了　(完了)＊"},{"pid":"fca87a4a229c1738d83da794a9b4a719a469add1","tid":2285891,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:32:51.000Z","msg":"撐侵大遊行就開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"babad2db61d664e657a22213263a6505430f426a","tid":2285891,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T05:01:05.000Z","msg":"天祐我侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}